# Technology Stack

| Layer           | Choice            | Rationale                              |
|-----------------|-------------------|----------------------------------------|
| Front-End       | React 18          | Mature ecosystem, hooks, community     |
| Bundler         | Vite              | Fast HMR, ESBuild underneath           |
| Styling         | Tailwind CSS      | Utility-first; design consistency      |
| State/Data      | TanStack Query    | Server-state cache, retries, suspense  |
| Back-End        | Supabase          | Postgres + Auth + Realtime out-of-box  |
| Serverless      | Supabase EdgeFns  | Deno-based; low-latency functions      |
| Storage         | Supabase Storage  | Built-in object store                  |
| External API    | Google Sheets v4  | Source of sales data for non-tech users|
| Tests (unit)    | Vitest            | Fast, Jest-compatible API              |
| Tests (e2e)     | Cypress           | Reliable browser automation            |
| CI/CD           | GitHub Actions    | Native, extensible, free minutes       |
| Monitoring      | Supabase Logs + Sentry | Application & error tracking     |
| Analytics       | PostHog           | Product analytics, self-host option    |

